<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="作品概要" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>作品概要</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">《钢之炼金术师》是由日本漫画家<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8D%92%E5%B7%9D%E5%BC%98">荒川弘</a>创作的漫画作品。2003年，<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%8F%B2%E5%85%8B%E5%A8%81%E5%B0%94%E8%89%BE%E5%B0%BC%E5%85%8B%E6%96%AF">史克威尔艾尼克斯</a>为提升旗下月刊杂志《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9C%88%E5%88%8A%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4GANGAN">月刊少年GANGAN</a>》的人气，决定将当时在该杂志上连载的《钢之炼金术师》动画化，并于同年7月发布制作动画版的消息。<div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:168px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/fd039245d688d43f8b33653b7f1ed21b0ff43b64?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:168px;height:220px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/-4o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=52784c48c91349547a1eef66664c92dd/fd039245d688d43f8b33653b7f1ed21b0ff43b64.jpg"  alt="" style="width:168px;height:220px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">2003年10月4日，由BONES制作，<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B0%B4%E5%B2%9B%E7%B2%BE%E4%BA%8C">水岛精二</a>任监督，会川昇任系列构成的动画版《钢之炼金术师》正式开播，在带动着《月刊少年GANGAN》的发行量稳步提升的同时，动画也取得前半平均收视率7%、后半平均收视率5%、最高收视率达8.4%的成绩<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="1" data-ctrmap=":1,">
[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_8509478">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">2004年10月2日，电视动画在播放完第51话后完结。随后，宣布本作动画的完结篇将以剧场版动画形式展现，由电视动画原班制作组继续负责制作。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">2005年7月23日，剧场版动画《钢之炼金术师：香巴拉的征服者》正式上映，本作动画宣告正式完结。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">由于本作动画企划时，原作漫画进度当时仅出版到单行本第5卷，于是后期部分剧情需要由原作者荒川弘提供漫画分镜稿给动画制作组说明场景<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="2" data-ctrmap=":2,">
[2]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[2]_8509478">&nbsp;</a>
，动画剧情前半以原作漫画单行本前7卷剧情为基础大幅改编，后半由于追上原作漫画连载进度，为避免与连载中的原作漫画出现相互冲突，转为向原创故事发展，所以动画在剧情发展、剧情设定以及部分人物设定上均与原作漫画有一定的不同。水岛监督认为，本作是原作漫画的“动画版二次作品”，是原作者所认可的另一部《钢之炼金术师》。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="剧情简介" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>剧情简介</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="2" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" title="动画海报"  href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/2491329/d058ccbf6c81800a90049eacb13533fa838b47aa?fr=lemma&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:177px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:175px;height:220px;">
<img class="picture" alt="动画海报" src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=f505af8201e9390152028a3c4bed54f9/d058ccbf6c81800a90049eacb13533fa838b47aa.jpg" style="width:175px;height:220px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
动画海报<span class="number">(40张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:169px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:163px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">故事发生在一个炼金术相当发达的世界，在这个世界的“炼金术”，是以理解物质的内在的法则：理解，分解，再构造成立，进行炼金术必须按照“等价交换”法则：为了获得某种东西，需要以同等的代价交换，代价不够的话便需要以自己的任何部份（身体的一部分、记忆等等）被作为代价的填补而被拿走。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%88%B1%E5%BE%B7%E5%8D%8E%C2%B7%E8%89%BE%E5%B0%94%E5%88%A9%E5%85%8B">爱德华·艾尔利克</a>和他弟弟<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%98%BF%E5%B0%94%E5%86%AF%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E8%89%BE%E5%B0%94%E5%88%A9%E5%85%8B">阿尔冯斯·艾尔利克</a>十分思念在他们还小的时候亡故的母亲，为了再次见到母亲，进行了炼金术中最大的禁忌——<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%93%E7%82%BC%E6%88%90">人体炼成</a>。可是因为炼成时的反噬，阿尔则失去了全身，爱德失去了左脚，为了换回弟弟，爱德华牺牲自己的右手作为代价将弟弟的灵魂炼成，并将弟弟阿尔冯斯的灵魂固定在一副铠甲上。从此爱德华和阿尔冯斯为了取回他们所失去的一切，开始踏上了找回自己身体的旅程。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">爱德华失去的右臂和左腿由钢制义肢“<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E9%93%A0">机械铠</a>”来替代，因此被授予“钢”的称号，故被称为“钢之炼金术师”。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="3" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="制作人员" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>制作人员</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="3" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<ul class="custom_dot  para-list list-paddingleft-1"><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">原作：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8D%92%E5%B7%9D%E5%BC%98">荒川弘</a>（史克威尔艾尼克斯《月刊少年GANGAN》连载）</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">导演：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B0%B4%E5%B2%9B%E7%B2%BE%E4%BA%8C">水岛精二</a></div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">企画：竹田青滋（每日放送）、田口浩司（史克威尔艾尼克斯）、胜股英夫（ANIPLEX）、高桥俊博（每日放送，第4话开始）</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">剧本统筹：会川昇</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">角色设计：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BC%8A%E8%97%A4%E5%98%89%E4%B9%8B">伊藤嘉之</a></div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">动画制片人：杉浦幸次、富冈隆司</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">制片设计：荒牧伸志</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">美术设计：成田伟保</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">美术设计助理：金平和茂</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">合成兽设计：石垣纯哉</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">美术监督：桥本和幸</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">色彩设计：中山しほ子</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">摄影监督：福士享</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">音响监督：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%89%E9%97%B4%E9%9B%85%E6%96%87">三间雅文</a></div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">音乐：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%A7%E5%B2%9B%E6%BB%A1">大岛满</a></div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">音乐制作：ANIPLEX</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">制片人：丸山博雄（每日放送）、南雅彦（BONES）、大山良（ANIPLEX）</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">制作：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E6%94%BE%E9%80%81">每日放送</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/ANIPLEX">ANIPLEX</a>、BONES</div>
</li></ul><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="4" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_4" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="角色介绍" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>角色介绍</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="4" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><i>※本词条角色介绍只限对<i>2003年版动画</i>登场的人物及剧情进行介绍，漫画原作人物及剧情介绍请点击漫画“</i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/38782" data-lemmaid="38782"><i>钢之炼金术师</i></a><i>”词条查看</i>。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>※【注：以下角色介绍包含剧透】</b></div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="4_1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_4_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="主要角色" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="4-1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>主要角色</h3>
</div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" width="99%" class="transparentBorder"><tr><td width="100" align="left" valign="middle"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/b8014a90f603738df3ed93eeb11bb051f919ec53?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=546eb129af6eddc422e7b3f909d9b6a2/b8014a90f603738df3ed93eeb11bb051f919ec53.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="para" label-module="para"><b><a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%88%B1%E5%BE%B7%E5%8D%8E%C2%B7%E8%89%BE%E5%B0%94%E5%88%A9%E5%85%8B">爱德华·艾尔利克</a></b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Edward Elric</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9C%B4%E7%92%90%E7%BE%8E">朴璐美</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">本作主人公，个子矮小的少年，12岁取得国家炼金术师资格，拥有“钢”之称号。右手与左脚为机械义肢，为了见到去世的母亲，和弟弟阿尔冯斯一起进行了人体炼成，结果失去了弟弟的身体与自己的手脚，为了找回失去的一切，与弟弟阿尔冯斯踏上寻找贤者之石的旅途。、</div>
</td></tr><tr><td width="100" align="left" valign="middle"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/b8014a90f603738df3ec93eeb11bb051f919ec5c?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:154px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=546fb129af6eddc422e7b3f909d9b6a2/b8014a90f603738df3ec93eeb11bb051f919ec5c.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:154px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="para" label-module="para"><b><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%98%BF%E5%B0%94%E5%86%AF%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E8%89%BE%E5%B0%94%E5%88%A9%E5%85%8B">阿尔冯斯·艾尔利克</a></b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Alphonse Elric</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%92%89%E5%AE%AB%E7%90%86%E6%83%A0">钉宫理惠</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">本作的另一个主人公，爱德华的弟弟，原本是个金发金眼的人类少年，因在尝试复活母亲使用人体炼成时失败，结果整个身体都被夺走，爱德以右臂为代价换回了他的灵魂，只能让灵魂寄生在冰冷的钢铁盔甲里。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/4bed2e738bd4b31ce1fd0b7785d6277f9f2ff83d?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=f1d77efb37fae6cd08b4ac633fb10f9e/4bed2e738bd4b31ce1fd0b7785d6277f9f2ff83d.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B8%A9%E8%8E%89%C2%B7%E6%B4%9B%E5%85%8B%E8%B4%9D%E5%B0%94"><b>温莉·洛克贝尔</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Winry Rockbell</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%B0%E5%8F%A3%E6%83%A0%E7%BE%8E">丰口惠美</a></div>
本作女主角，失去了父母的她从小和祖母一起生活，与爱德和阿尔青梅竹马。对机械铠和跟机械铠有关的一切事物感兴趣，与祖母比拿可一样成为机械铠工程师，是爱德的专属技师。对艾尔利克兄弟来说是等同于家人的重要存在，为了能帮助一直在进行旅行的艾尔利克兄弟，努力提升自己，想让自己做出更好的机械铠，是个相当坚强而内心温柔的女孩。</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/bd3eb13533fa828ba2be022fff1f4134960a5a58?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/-4o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=bcaed11056e736d15c138b0aab524ffc/bd3eb13533fa828ba2be022fff1f4134960a5a58.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%9C%8D%E6%81%A9%E6%B5%B7%E5%A7%86"><b>霍恩海姆<b></b></b></a><b><b>·艾尔利克</b></b><div class="para" label-module="para">Hohenheim Elric</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B1%9F%E5%8E%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%A3%AB">江原正士</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">400年前成功制造出贤者之石，能将灵魂转移到另一人的身体继续生存，可是在一次进行灵魂转移，失去抵抗肉体恶化，但丁400年前相恋的对象，并将而让你死去的炼成人造人。因不希望让妻子夏看见开始腐烂的身体，所以便离她而去。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/96dda144ad34598273b17b5e0ef431adcaef84c7?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=c8f13bae9a22720e7fcee5f84bca0a3a/96dda144ad34598273b17b5e0ef431adcaef84c7.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BC%8A%E5%85%B9%E7%B1%B3%C2%B7%E5%8D%A1%E8%BF%AA%E6%96%AF"><b>伊兹米·卡迪斯</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Izumi Curtis</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B4%A5%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%A0%E5%AD%90">津田匠子</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">但丁的弟子，为了让死去的孩子复活，她触犯了禁忌，进行人体炼成因而失去身体的一部分，不能再生育。至此之后也让她下定不轻易使用炼金术的决心。但是被艾尔利克兄弟真挚眼神打动的她，成为了两兄弟的师傅。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/8c1001e93901213f6822d01056e736d12e2e95ed?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=3bd4b1b0530fd9f9a417526b152cd42b/8c1001e93901213f6822d01056e736d12e2e95ed.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%A1"><b>斯卡</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Scar</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%BD%AE%E9%B2%87%E9%BE%99%E5%A4%AA%E9%83%8E">置鲇龙太郎</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">伊修巴尔人，因为额头有交叉伤痕，因而被称作“伤疤人”（斯卡即Scar，并非本名）。右手是他哥哥留给他的未完成的贤者之石，可以爆炸破坏任何物质，为了向金布利证明人类体内不是空空如也而分解自己的左手。</div>
</td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="4_2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_4_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="军方人员" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="4-2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>军方人员</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b></b></div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" class="transparentBorder" data-sort="sortDisabled"><tr><td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/f11f3a292df5e0fe6e9223cc5e6034a85fdf7271?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=47c9557d67380cd7e21ea5ef9146ad14/f11f3a292df5e0fe6e9223cc5e6034a85fdf7271.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%BD%97%E4%BC%8A%C2%B7%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6"><b>罗伊·马斯坦</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Roy Mustang</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%A7%E5%B7%9D%E9%80%8F">大川透</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">上校军衔，拥有‘焰’之称号的国家级炼金术师，杀害温莉父母的凶手，在东方司令部的军队任职。私底下处处保护着艾尔利克兄弟。在挚友死后，马斯坦古开始暗中调查他被杀的原因，得知了“贤者之石”的真相。。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/d52a2834349b033be894691717ce36d3d439bddb?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=c8d5aa2c60d9f2d3241123ed99ed8a53/d52a2834349b033be894691717ce36d3d439bddb.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8E%89%E8%8E%8E%C2%B7%E9%9C%8D%E5%85%8B%E8%89%BE"><b>莉莎·霍克艾</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Riza Hawkeye</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%A0%B9%E8%B0%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%99%BA%E5%AD%90">根谷美智子</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">中尉军衔，效命于东方司令部，马斯坦的副官，她总是陪伴在罗伊身边处理事务。有着远超于常人的高超枪法于时刻沉着冷静的性格，在加上不留情面的率真与语气，令周围人对她又怕又敬，跟随马斯坦出生入死到最后。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/728da9773912b31bd8be67e48418367adbb4e129?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=b52bce2783cb39dbc5c06054e01409a7/728da9773912b31bd8be67e48418367adbb4e129.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E4%BC%91%E6%96%AF"><b>马斯·休斯</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Maes Hughes</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%97%A4%E5%8E%9F%E5%90%AF%E6%B2%BB">藤原启治</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">中校军衔，中央军阀会议所任职，和罗伊是多年的老友，是个非常爱老婆和孩子的好男人。看上去吊儿郎当，但头脑反应极快，对遇到困难的人总是忍不住伸出援手。因协助艾尔利克兄弟调查第五研究所而无意间发现了人造人的秘密。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/cb8065380cd791235ff301b9af345982b3b780e8?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=a50cefb722a446237acaa260a8237246/cb8065380cd791235ff301b9af345982b3b780e8.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BA%9A%E5%8A%9B%E5%85%8B%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E8%B7%AF%E6%98%93%C2%B7%E9%98%BF%E5%A7%86%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97"><b>亚力克斯·路易·阿姆斯特朗</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Alex Louis Armstrong</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%86%85%E6%B5%B7%E8%B4%A4%E4%BA%8C">内海贤二</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">少校军衔，有着‘豪腕’之称号的国家级炼金术师，只有一个妹妹。炽热到沸腾的肌肉体魄，总是毫无意义地热血男儿情，以及动不动就热泪的魄力。后配合马斯坦在北方发动兵变。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/4bed2e738bd4b31cf736017685d6277f9f2ff8f1?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=e71c74fa37fae6cd08b4ac633fb20f9e/4bed2e738bd4b31cf736017685d6277f9f2ff8f1.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%87%91%C2%B7%E5%B8%83%E6%8B%89%E5%BE%B7%E9%9B%B7"><b>金·布拉德雷</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">King Bradley</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9F%B4%E7%94%B0%E7%A7%80%E8%83%9C">柴田秀胜</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">大总统，立下汗马功劳而成为独裁者，指挥大规模的歼灭作战，四处发动战争，将人推向绝望的深渊，从而产生贤者之石的原材料和制造者。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
