</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9%C2%B7%E6%A0%BC%E5%85%B0"><b>马斯特·格兰</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Basque Grand</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：青森伸</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">大总统的左右手之一，铁血无情，可炼成包覆全身的多管炮座攻击。在伊修瓦尔内乱时，要求马可医生提供贤者之石试作品给各国家炼金术师，作为炼成增幅剂，向马斯坦古下令处决温莉的父母。实际上第五研究所的负责人。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/9f510fb30f2442a79f396868d343ad4bd01302c3?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=764485e297cad1c8d4bbfb254f3f67c4/9f510fb30f2442a79f396868d343ad4bd01302c3.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BD%90%E5%B0%94%E5%A4%AB%C2%B7J%C2%B7%E9%87%91%E5%B8%83%E5%88%A9"><b>佐尔夫·J·金布利</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Solf J. Kimblee</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%8A%E7%94%B0%E7%A5%90%E5%8F%B8">上田祐司</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">中校，有着‘红莲’之称号的国家级炼金术师，原为地方军队所属的军人，喜欢使用炼金术将人体变成炸弹。杀死斯卡哥哥和在斯卡前额留下伤痕的凶手。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/4034970a304e251f804c7135a586c9177e3e5347?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=5a44759f8735e5dd942ca2dd46c7a7f5/4034970a304e251f804c7135a586c9177e3e5347.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><b>法兰克·亚伽</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Frank Archer</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%80%9F%E6%B0%B4%E5%A5%96">速水奖</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">继任死去的休斯中校一职。向大总统提出了作为战争武器投入合成兽的人。后晋升为上校，在斯卡的炼成阵里失去一半身体，因而身体的一半机械化。</div>
</td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="4_3" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_4_3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="人造人" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="4-3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>人造人</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b></b></div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" class="transparentBorder" data-sort="sortDisabled"><tr><td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/060828381f30e924c67532fd4e086e061c95f72d?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=a7df5369d343ad4ba22e41c2b2005a89/060828381f30e924c67532fd4e086e061c95f72d.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BD%86%E4%B8%81/7933056" data-lemmaid="7933056"><b>但丁</b></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Dante</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%89%E5%B1%B1%E4%BD%B3%E5%AF%BF%E5%AD%90">杉山佳寿子</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">指挥并支配人造人的幕后黑手。伊兹米的老师，霍恩海姆400年前相恋的对象。从400年前转移身体后变得长寿，但在灵魂转移过程中由于灵魂的劣化肉体会老化。为了进行灵魂转移，需要贤者之石的力量，因此她透过人造人的活动在暗地里控制人类社会，借由发动战争而使人们陷入绝望并追寻贤者之石的力量，通过隐藏贤者之石的真相而引导那些寻求者完成贤者之石的制作。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/c2fdfc039245d688e4bc1b68a6c27d1ed31b24bb?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=042bc2238fb1cb133a693b11ed5556da/c2fdfc039245d688e4bc1b68a6c27d1ed31b24bb.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%8B%89%E4%B8%9D%E7%89%B9"><b>拉丝特</b></a><b>（色欲）</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Lust</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BD%90%E8%97%A4%E4%BD%91%E5%AD%90">佐藤佑子</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">原为斯卡的哥哥的恋人，十多年前斯卡的哥哥为了复活恋人而进行人体炼成的产物，后被但丁接收并任命为第二代拉丝特，心如蛇蝎，但一直希望能成为真正的人类。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/ca1349540923dd5454580ca4d309b3de9d8248d6?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=d2b4920833adcbef053479049cae2e0e/ca1349540923dd5454580ca4d309b3de9d8248d6.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%A0%BC%E5%88%A9%E5%BE%B7"><b>格利德</b></a><b>（贪婪）</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Greed</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%AF%B9%E8%AE%BF%E9%83%A8%E9%A1%BA%E4%B8%80">诹访部顺一</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">原为爱慕但丁的青年，死后被但丁以血红之石进行人体炼成的产物。虽由但丁亲手制造，但不想受限于血红之石，渴望永恒的生命而背叛，于是掳走阿尔想要研究想获得长生不老的生命，但结果遭金布利跟塔卡背叛和拉丝特跟格拉托尼的追杀。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/2fdda3cc7cd98d10db63a7fd233fb80e7aec9043?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=b1ea92cf8544ebf86971633de9f8d736/2fdda3cc7cd98d10db63a7fd233fb80e7aec9043.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%AF%E6%B4%9B%E6%96%AF"><b>斯洛斯</b></a><b>（怠惰）</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Sloth</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%B9%B0%E6%A3%AE%E6%B7%91%E4%B9%83">鹰森淑乃</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">原为艾尔利克兄弟为使母亲复活而进行人体炼成的产物，被但丁找出且喂食血红之石，可化为液状游走，顶替在伊修瓦尔内乱前两年死亡的茱丽叶·道格拉斯上尉身份，以大总统秘书官身份在军部活动。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/574e9258d109b3de9a294fa4cebf6c81810a4c63?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=70a2d5caaeaf2eddd0f14eebbd120102/574e9258d109b3de9a294fa4cebf6c81810a4c63.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%A0%BC%E6%8B%89%E6%89%98%E5%B0%BC"><b>格拉托尼</b></a><b>（暴食）</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Gluttony</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%AB%98%E6%88%B7%E9%9D%96%E5%B9%BF">高户靖广</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">原为但丁制造血红之石的产物。拉丝特死后，但丁为控制意识混乱的格拉托尼，消去其舌头上的衔尾蛇刺青，使他只会为了食欲而行动。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/78310a55b319ebc4ebf4dd558026cffc1f171669?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/-4o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=9f7f5d01fe039245a5b5e60db796a4a8/78310a55b319ebc4ebf4dd558026cffc1f171669.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%81%A9%E7%BB%B4"><b>恩维</b></a><b>（嫉妒</b>）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Envy</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B1%B1%E5%8F%A3%E7%9C%9F%E5%BC%93">山口真弓</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">原为霍恩海姆及但丁两人因汞中毒而死去之子，霍恩海姆为使他复活而进行了人体炼成，有着喜欢欺骗夺取伤害他人的残虐个性，因认为霍恩海姆抛弃了自己而对他和艾尔利克兄弟产生嫉恨，一直都在追杀霍恩海姆。声称已经忘记原来的样子，常以黑长发少年的外貌出现。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/d043ad4bd11373f0cce3c453a60f4bfbfaed0419?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=31dff9f5cb3d70cf48faad0fc8ded1ba/d043ad4bd11373f0cce3c453a60f4bfbfaed0419.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF"><b>拉斯</b></a><b>（愤怒）</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Wrath</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B0%B4%E6%A0%91%E5%A5%88%E5%A5%88">水树奈奈</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">原是伊兹米死去的婴儿，送入“门”内进行人体炼成，其后独自从门里逃出，被但丁接收为人造人，把斯洛斯当作母亲。在爱德杀死斯洛斯后，要求但丁复活斯洛斯却反遭切除原不属他的手足，在被温莉装上机械铠后去向不明。由于身上有着爱德身上右臂和左腿，因而可以使用炼金术，可将其他物质与自己的身体融合。</div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/d058ccbf6c81800a122a22c2b33533fa838b472a?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:160px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=772b13ec03e9390152028a3c4bee54f9/d058ccbf6c81800a122a22c2b33533fa838b472a.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:160px;"/>
</a>
</div></div>
</td><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><div class="para" label-module="para"><b><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%99%AE%E8%8E%B1%E5%BE%B7">普莱德</a>（傲慢）</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Pride</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">配音：<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9F%B4%E7%94%B0%E7%A7%80%E8%83%9C">柴田秀胜</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">大总统金<b>·</b>布拉德雷，但丁引以自豪的“杰作”，可看见空气的流动，同样有者再生能力。在但丁授意下四处发动战争，将人推向绝望的深渊，从而产生贤者之石的原材料和制造者。</div>
</td></tr></table><div class="para" label-module="para"><sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="3" data-ctrmap=":3,">
[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_8509478">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="5" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_5" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="背景设定" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>背景设定</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="5" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><i>※本词条背景设定只限对<i>2003年版动画</i>中背景设定进行解释介绍，原作漫画<i>背景设定</i>介绍请点击漫画“</i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/38782" data-lemmaid="38782"><i>钢之炼金术师</i></a><i>”词条查看。</i></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b><b>亚美斯特利斯</b></b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/0/11385343fbf2b2118900fa9bca8065380cd78e3c?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="亚美斯特利斯地图" style="width:220px;height:194px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=3c84130b3d6d55fbc1c671245d234f40/11385343fbf2b2118900fa9bca8065380cd78e3c.jpg"  alt="亚美斯特利斯地图" style="width:220px;height:194px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
亚美斯特利斯地图
</span>
</div>由军政府统治的国家，大陆历1558年左右建国，现任大总统金·布拉德雷。国土近呈圆形，分为五大地区，以中央区域为中心，各在东、南、西、北四个地区设立司令部，负责管理当地的军事、行政，并操控形同傀儡的议会及法院。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>中央市</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b></b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">位于亚美斯多利斯的中心，亚美斯多利斯的首都，大总统府、炼金术研究所、中央司令部、宪兵司令部和中央监狱等都设于此地。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>大总统府 </b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">中央司令部腹地内国军最高机关，可经走廊通往官邸。直辖炼金术研究机关、国家炼金术师机关。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>大总统官邸</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">位于中央市郊外的瓦古地区，大总统居住的地方。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>第三研究所 </b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">马可医生之前隶属的研究单位，研究所底下可能有通往大总统府的地道。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>第五研究所 </b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">已废弃的炼金术研究所，位于中央监狱旁，实际上是炼成贤者之石及研究合成兽的地方。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>中央监狱 </b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">位于第五研究所旁，收监重要犯人的场所。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>国立中央图书馆 </b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">国内最大的藏书所在地，国家炼金术师可查阅特殊文件的地方。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>地下设施 </b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">但丁的地下都市，出入口在旧市区废弃基督教大教堂。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>东都</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">东方司令部所在，罗伊·马斯坦的原驻地，司令官为古拉曼中将。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>利塞布尔</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">艾尔利克兄弟及温莉的故乡，盛行牧羊的小村庄。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>里欧尔</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">东部边境市镇，太阳神雷托教主柯奈洛行奇迹之术蛊惑群众，后续引发暴乱，后被斯卡用作贤者之石炼成阵。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>阿库罗亚</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">水之都，有名的观光胜地，怪盗“赛壬”出没的城镇。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>杰诺塔姆</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">黄金产地，曾是繁极一时的城镇，马古瓦尔研究“贤者之石”的地方。<b></b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>海德</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">马可医生逃亡后藏身的小村庄。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>伊修巴尔</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">位于东南方的前自治区，在伊修瓦尔内乱爆发后，被撤销自治。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>尤斯威尔</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">接邻东方大沙漠的产煤矿场，被称为“极东城镇”。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>纽奥布丁</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">哈库洛少将曾任职的军方支部驻地。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>西都</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">西方司令部所在地。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>达普利斯</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">南方司令部所在地，避暑胜地，卡迪斯夫妇经营的肉店、格利德的“恶魔之巢”酒吧都在此。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>奇修亚</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">在达普利斯以南。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>拉修巴雷</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">机械铠技师的圣地，随着义肢技术发达而繁荣起来的地方。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>卡乌罗伊湖</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">达普利斯的附近，著名的旅游胜地。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>约克岛</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">卡乌罗伊湖湖心小岛，艾尔利克兄弟幼年修行的地方。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>北都</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">北方司令部所在地。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>布里克兹</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">亚美斯多利斯最北疆，与德拉古马交界的山脉，有“天险”之称，在此设立布里克斯要塞。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>阿耶鲁戈</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">位于亚美斯多利斯南方的国家。双方曾爆发过两次国境战争，现仍断断续续交战中。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>德拉古马</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">位于亚美斯多利斯北方的大国，被亚美斯多利斯认为是蛮族国家。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>东国</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">位于亚美斯多利斯东方，东方大沙漠中曾经有过的繁荣王国，霍恩海姆跟但丁将全国人民炼成贤者之石。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="6" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_6" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="用语解释" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>用语解释</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="6" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b></b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><i>※本词条用语解释只限对<i>2003年版动画</i>中用语进行解释介绍，原作漫画用语解释介绍请点击漫画“</i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/38782" data-lemmaid="38782"><i>钢之炼金术师</i></a><i>”词条查看。</i></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>军部</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">亚美斯多利斯军政府体制的统称，军队被称为“国军”，并由宪兵负责警察的工作。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>先士</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">亚美斯多利斯的货币单位，币值与日圆相当。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>大陆历</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">亚美斯多利斯所使用的纪年。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>国家炼金术师</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">亚美斯多利斯为奖励国家炼金术的研究，优秀术师经考试合格者，授予国家炼金术师资格。国家炼金术师的三大限制分别是“不可炼人”、“不可炼黄金”和“必须绝对效忠军方”。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>生体炼成</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">亚美斯多利斯以身体受伤部份再生为治疗目的合法许可生物相关炼成，有别于“人体炼成”而称为“生体炼成”的医疗行为。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>合成兽</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">动物与动物合成实验的产物，合法许可生物相关炼成但用人当材料的人体实验或与动物合成则是违法的。实际上，军部秘密进行人与动物合成研究已有成果。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>人体炼成</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">国家炼金法三大限制之一“不可炼人”。人是由肉体、灵魂、精神三要素组成，精神连系着肉体和灵魂。如对死者进行人体炼成则缺少灵魂导致失败，而活人因三要素俱在，可一度分解、再构筑进行人体炼成。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>人造人</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">人体炼成失败产物，所以只有肉体和精神而没有灵魂，需贤者之石未完成品“血红之石”发展成形。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>机械铠</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">义肢的进化型态，以神经末梢电讯号的传送接口、及驱动关节的轴承所构成，因此无法连接到中枢神经，不可能全身机械铠化、内藏或作脏器用途，材质则需安定的金属。而人体神经末梢最敏感，在装上机械铠连接时，会伴随超乎异常的刺痛，在复健阶段也十分难受。基本上作为医疗用途，也可用在动物上。除了技师的个性化设计外，还有改造、内藏武器等多样化的机械铠。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>门</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">人体炼成时，在炼成阵中心出现的门，门另一端为现实世界，门在每个人体内，除人体炼成外，肉体、灵魂及精神联系脆弱的婴儿更容易开启。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>真理</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">可称“真理”、“世界”、“宇宙”、“神”，即是“一”也为“全”的存在；以对应施术者的透明外型出现在真理之门前，之后显示其付出的“通行费”。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>炼金术</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">一种能够改变物质的构成与外形，并且制造出另一种物质的技术。基本原则是等价交换，原材料与炼成的物质的质量与元素与必须是相同的，所以无法用水炼出金属。不过因为大地中有多种金属元素（铝、铁等），所以大多数格斗派的炼金术师都可以就地取材，制造出多种武器。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">亚美斯多利斯的炼金术以军用为主，曾经在伊修瓦尔内乱中投入国家炼金术师作为兵器，对战争的提早胜利起了重要作用。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">炼成的过程分为三步：理解、分解、再构成。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>“一即是全、全即是一”</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">“世上一切都由一产生，一切都会回归一，即是一为全；一中有全、全中有一，如一中无全，全即则无。”</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>炼成阵</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">启动炼金术力量的构筑式。基本就是圆的力量，圆表示力的循环，在圆中画出构筑式，送入施术者的意念，即可发动炼成阵的力量、进行炼成。炼成阵的构筑式除基本圆形外，因炼金术师的不同、而有图案及文字的不同。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>贤者之石炼成阵</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">由圆、正六角形组合的炼成阵；精制贤者之石必须靠爆发力压缩，则改成圆、正七角形。两者交点上放置血红之水，将人柱置于阵内。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>等价交换</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">炼金术的基本法则，如果要得到某样东西，就必须要付出同等的代价。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>贤者之石</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">传说中可以无视“等价交换”原则的术法增幅器，需大量的人柱，并参杂那一刻爆发的怨恨、仇恨和愤怒才能精制出来，否则是成为不完全品“血红之石”。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>人柱</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">炼成贤者之石所需的活人祭品，不只是灵魂、连肉体也一并当成材料。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>炼金研究书</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">炼金术师会用暗号书写炼金研究书或手册。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="7" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_7" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="剧集信息" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>剧集信息</h2>
