</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>相关产品</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="10" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="10_1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_10_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="剧场版" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="10-1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>剧场版</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b></b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><sub>主词条：《钢之炼金术师：香巴拉的征服者》</sub></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">由BONES制作，水岛精二任监督，会川昇任脚本，于2005年7月23日在日本上映，该作的剧情延续动画剧情，讲述了爱德华·艾尔利克穿过真理之门，来到无法使用炼金术的另一个世界的故事。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="10_2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub8509478_10_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="DVD" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="10-2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">钢之炼金术师</span>DVD</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">从2003年12月17日开始发行销售第一卷，至2005年1月26日发行销售最后一卷，全13卷，收录电视播放全51话。DVD与剧场版全卷累计销量达100万<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="12" data-ctrmap=":12,">
[12]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[12]_8509478">&nbsp;</a>
。<a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" title="DVD封面"  href="/pic/%E9%92%A2%E4%B9%8B%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%88/1600763/13051935/3b292df5e0fe99258eca399936a85edf8cb17130?fr=lemma&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:221px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:219px;height:167px;">
<img class="picture" alt="DVD封面" src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/c0%3Dbaike60%2C5%2C5%2C60%2C20/sign=9b17efea612762d09433acedc185639f/3b292df5e0fe99258eca399936a85edf8cb17130.jpg" style="width:219px;height:167px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
DVD封面<span class="number">(13张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:213px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:207px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
